# NOTE: alerts/ holds SOURCE code (teams.py, email.py) the app imports —
# do NOT ignore the whole folder. Only its __pycache__ is ignored (above).

# Keep the db/ directory in the repo even though its contents are ignored
!db/.gitkeep

# ── Excel / Office files ──────────────────────────────────────────
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.xlsm
*.csv
# Word/Excel temporary lock files
~$*

# ── Root-level legacy HTML copies (not used — ui/ is the live path) ──
